We are to define and implement the queue behaviour using stacks.

Queue behavior is first-in-first-out(fifo) and stack behaviour is las-in-first-out. So we use two stacks one is input stack which will store the stack behavior and
then we pop values into the other stack which will reverse the first stack to provide queue behavior.


